snippet: The Washington Square Music Festival presented “Music and Poetry in Greenwich Village” with the West Village Chorale Tuesday night at St. Joseph’s Church.
abstract: Steve Smith reviews performances by the West Village Chorale and the Festival Chamber Ensemble at St Joseph's Roman Catholic Church as part of the Washington Square Music Festival.
lead_paragraph: The Washington Square Music Festival presented “Music and Poetry in Greenwich Village” with the West Village Chorale Tuesday night at St. Joseph’s Church.
